01:11:23.788 --> 01:11:27.368
The key foundation in all of that will be achieving net negative

1254
01:11:27.408 --> 01:11:28.948
emissions.

1255
01:11:31.088 --> 01:11:35.028
We fear under the bill that climate and environment will be submerged in

1256
01:11:35.068 --> 01:11:38.998
the new MCERT, while the CEO will have the title of Secretary for

1257
01:11:39.068 --> 01:11:42.628
the Environment. In practice, based on the budget allocations of

