Thank you, Madam Chair. We welcome any questions.

1290
01:13:33.464 --> 01:13:37.064
Thank you very much, Fred. Look, you have met time with that

1291
01:13:37.144 --> 01:13:39.904
submission, so there aren't any further questions.

