01:14:19.844 --> 01:14:23.514
We'll just wait for Simon, the commissioner, to pop up.

1303
01:14:23.704 --> 01:14:24.624
He was there.

1304
01:14:24.644 --> 01:14:27.084
He popped up and then popped away again.

1305
01:14:29.584 --> 01:14:31.464
Keeps coming and going. You have a problem.

1306
01:14:32.564 --> 01:14:33.964
There we go. Welcome, Commissioner,

1307
01:14:35.004 --> 01:14:37.384
and welcome all to the select committee.

